                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;In strictly POSIX shells this can be a tricky problem because you don&apos;t have here strings or process substitutions to avoid the pipe. &lt;a href=&quot;http://mywiki.wooledge.org/BashFAQ/024&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;BashFAQ 24&lt;/a&gt; has some useful solutions even in that case.&lt;/span&gt;

